<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><aka>I worship You, almighty God</aka>
<key>E</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 I worship You, almighty God;
 There is none like You.
 I worship You, oh Prince of Peace,
 that is what I want to do.
 And I give You praise;
 For You are my righteousness,
 I worship You, almighty God;
 There is none like You.

[V2]
 Jeg tilber Deg, Allmektig Gud,
 ingen er som Du.
 Jeg tilber Deg, O Fredsfyrste,
 Det er hva jeg ønsker nu.
 Og jeg gir Deg all pris;
 for Du er min rettferdighet,
 Jeg tilber Deg, allmektig Gud,
 ingen er som Du.</lyrics>
<title>Jeg tilber Deg</title>
<presentation>v1 v2 </presentation>
</song>